prompts.prompt: In a distant galaxy far away, Nikh the Elephant, Ant, Dog, and Football lived on the planet Zorbon. They were best friends and spent their days exploring the vast space landscapes filled with colorful stars and unknown planets.

One day, as they were playing catch with Football, they noticed a strange spaceship crash-landing nearby. Curious, they approached the spaceship and found a small alien creature trapped inside. The alien communicated that it needed help fixing its spaceship to return home.

Working together, Nikh, Ant, Dog, and Football used their unique skills to repair the spaceship and bid farewell to the grateful alien. As they watched the spaceship soar back into space, they realized that even in the vastness of the universe, friendship and teamwork could overcome any challenge.
